reviewText: A great collection of Lifetime Movies at a very reasonable price. Lifetime Channel seems to have changed drastically over the years, and there are very few quality movies on that station anymore, so I am glad that I can purchase these thrillers and dramas at such a great cost!
Great movies, love lifetime movies! I'm so glad I found these. I hope everyone enjoys them as much as I did!

Valerie Bertenelli is amazing and scary in her true life movie of a schizophrenic. Delta plays a scared mama of a real punk of a son, and the other story is pretty good, but I mainly got it for Val and Delta.
i really love it and i am glad that i found one i have been  looking for a while for this movie
Have not watched these movies as of yet.  I am sure I will thoroughly enjoy them when I do watch them.

Two out of three movies where excellent. The Ultimate Betrayal lingered on too much and didn't have good writing. But the other movies where exactly like lifetimes are. Very good! I would recommend this collection.

these films was very moving, and  heart breaking. Murder of innocence A very ill person,Who no one seen  until she married and the husband tried to get every one to see how dangerous she was. It shows parents need to observe their childrens  behavior  from birth to better help them to adulthood.

All 3 of these movies was really very good,Insights on what you could do  to better help  or get help for a family member. Great movies
